dcat:dataset.dct:title: Environmental Health Operational Areas (simplify10m)
dcat:dataset.dct:description:
Operational Areas within the Environmental Health Section of The Highland Council - North Highland, Mid Highland and West Highland. Please note that this is a slightly generalised version of the boundaries.

Gemini metadata  record is at:
https://www.spatialdata.gov.scot/geonetwork/srv/eng/catalog.search#/metadata/29f4dc28-5a56-4fad-b27e-12b74e159a17

dcat:dataset.dct:title: Flare Zones (simplify10m)
dcat:dataset.dct:description:
Flare Zones within the Highland Council Area. A Flare Zone is an administrative area referred to within the operations for Environmental Health. Flare is the Information Management System used within the Environmental Health Function of The Highland Council - this database is also known as CIVICA APP. Please note that this is a slightly generalised version of the boundaries.

Gemini metadata  record is at:
https://www.spatialdata.gov.scot/geonetwork/srv/eng/catalog.search#/metadata/{4c20561e-1a50-4a7b-b4eb-98e2af45a00a}

dcat:dataset.dct:title: Operational Areas (historical 1999 to 2007)
dcat:dataset.dct:description:
The 8 historical Operational Areas from 1999-2007 - ie. Caithness, Sutherland, Ross & Cromarty, Skye & Lochalsh, Inverness, Nairn, Lochaber, Badenoch & Strathspey.

Full dataset- ie. not simplified version.

Gemini metadata record is at https://www.spatialdata.gov.scot/geonetwork/srv/eng/catalog.search#/metadata/40bb2aba-98ee-4509-ae08-41badcdf9018

Created by uploading zipped .shp.

dcat:dataset.dct:title: Private Water Supplies
dcat:dataset.dct:description: This dataset contains the location details of Type A and Type B Private Water Supplies known of by The Highland Council within The Highland Council Area. There are likely to be private water supplies that the council has not been notified of and so are not yet recorded in this dataset but they will be added when the council is made aware of them. Gemini metadata record is at https://www.spatialdata.gov.scot/geonetwork/srv/eng/catalog.search#/metadata/%7Bf7b4d832-1712-4c53-864e-0e755e0873ef%7D
